# FLAGS:
# -finit-local-zero: initialize local INTEGER, REAL, and COMPLEX variables to zero, LOGICAL variables to false, and CHARACTER variables to a string of null bytes.
# mcmodel=large: Generate code for the large model: This model makes no assumptions about addresses and sizes of sections.
# O2: performs nearly all supported optimizations that do not involve a space-speed tradeoff.
mpifort -std=legacy -O2 -o mpisolvetomo mpisolvetomo.f
